        <p>I&#39;ve seen this on here a while back and enjoyed it then and again now. I don&#39;t remember if I passed it to my children so I made sure I did this time.<br />
Thank you for sharing.<br />
<br />
It is how I felt yesterday. I saved 1 spoon Sunday and used all my spoons yesterday so I could be with my grandbaby, do a couple of errands, dine and see a foolish dr, 2 hr ride each way. Was asleep before 9pm, woke at 4am and will go back to bed 10-11am for a nice rest.</p>
