        <p>So far the remicade is working great for me!, it doesn&#39;t necessarily help the pain, but it does help that awful sick/hungover feeling that I used to live with everyday, and that initself is worth its weight in gold!! (well actually it already costs almost that!! :) )  I hope it starts doing more though, my pulmonary doesn&#39;t think it is doing enough and wants to pull the plug, thankfully my rheumy has the final say, and after me pleading my case, that it was my body, my life and I wanted to stay on it and it should be my say. he kept me on it. My fingers are crossed.    Tee</p>
