    <h3>Help and information from FSR</h3>
    <div class="generic-sidebar">
        <p>
            <a href="http://www.stopsarcoidosis.org/sarcoidosis/symptoms.htm" rel="ext"><img src="/resources/partners/fsr/groups/stop-sarcoidosis/images/sarcoidosis-body.jpg" alt="Sarcoidosis and the Body" class="left"/></a>
            <br/>
            Sarcoidosis is a "multiorgan" disease - meaning it almost always involves more than one organ. It's unpredictable and affects different people in different ways.
            <br/><br/>
            You can learn about the ways in which sarcoidosis affects the body in FSR's <a href="http://www.stopsarcoidosis.org/sarcoidosis/symptoms.htm">Sarcoidosis and the Body</a> brochure.
        </p>
        <div class="clear"></div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="http://www.stopsarcoidosis.org/sarcoidosis/diseasefacts.htm" rel="ext">Learn the basics from FSR</a></li>
