            <li><a href="http://www.stopsarcoidosis.org/store/" rel="ext">Order awareness materials</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://www.stopsarcoidosis.org/ecommerce/donate/donate-amount.htm" rel="ext">Donate: Help FSR fund new programs</a></li>
